  <main>
    <div class="main__slide" id="slide0">
      <p>
        In unexpected moments,
        like a sudden collapse, an accident, or a drowning situation,
        knowledge of CPR can make the difference between life and death.
        Learning these skills is an investment in everyone's safety and well-being.
      </p>
      <div class="main__slide--buttons">
        <a href="./index.html" class="back btn"><i class='bx bx-left-arrow-alt'></i></a>
        <a href="#slide1" class="next btn"><i class='bx bx-right-arrow-alt'></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main__slide" id="slide1">
      <div>
        <div class="main__slide--head">
          <span>1</span>
          <h3>Initial Assessment</h3>
        </div>
        <!--https://www.cigna.com/es-us/knowledge-center/hw/maniobra-de-heimlich-para-adultos-y-para-nios-de-tf7235-->
        <p>
          First, let's assess the victim's condition. Do they respond? Are they breathing normally?
          Are they conscious? If the answer is negative to any of these questions,
          it's time to take action.
        </p>
      </div>
      <img src="../../aprende-a-salvar-vidas/img/image11.jpg" alt="" />
      <div class="main__slide--buttons">
        <a href="#slide0" class="back btn"><i class='bx bx-left-arrow-alt'></i></a>
        <a href="#slide2" class="next btn"><i class='bx bx-right-arrow-alt'></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main__slide" id="slide2">
      <div>
        <div class="main__slide--head">
          <span>2</span>
          <h3>Call for Emergency</h3>
        </div>
        <p>
          Call the emergency number corresponding to your location or ask someone else to do so.
          Make sure you always have this number on hand.
        </p>
      </div>
      <img src="../../aprende-a-salvar-vidas/img/image12.jpg" alt="" />
      <div class="main__slide--buttons">
        <a href="#slide1" class="back btn"><i class='bx bx-left-arrow-alt'></i></a>
        <a href="#slide3" class="next btn"><i class='bx bx-right-arrow-alt'></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main__slide" id="slide3">
      <div>
        <div class="main__slide--head">
          <span>3</span>
          <h3>Correct Position</h3>
        </div>
        <p>
          Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation (CPR) begins with the proper position:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Kneel beside the victim's chest.</li>
          <li>Place the heel of one hand in the center of the sternum.</li>
          <li>Put the other hand on top of the first hand, interlocking your fingers.</li>
          <li>Make sure not to touch the victim's ribs.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <img src="../../aprende-a-salvar-vidas/img/image15.jpg" alt="" />
      <div class="main__slide--buttons">
        <a href="#slide2" class="back btn"><i class='bx bx-left-arrow-alt'></i></a>
        <a href="#slide4" class="next btn"><i class='bx bx-right-arrow-alt'></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main__slide" id="slide4">
      <div>
        <!-- https://www.ludusglobal.com/blog/como-hacer-la-maniobra-de-heimlich -->
        <div class="main__slide--head">
          <span>4</span>
          <h3>Practical Application</h3>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Keep your arms straight and use your body weight to apply pressure to your hands.</li>
          <li>Perform downward compressions, pushing the person's chest down by 5 to 6 cm.</li>
          <li>Perform 30 uninterrupted compressions.</li>
          <li>Repeat this cycle 5 times.</li>
          <li>You should achieve between 100 and 120 compressions per minute.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <img src="../../aprende-a-salvar-vidas/img/image14.jpg" alt="" />
      <div class="main__slide--buttons">
        <a href="#slide3" class="back btn"><i class='bx bx-left-arrow-alt'></i></a>
        <a href="#slide5" class="next btn"><i class='bx bx-right-arrow-alt'></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main__slide" id="slide5">
      <div>
        <div class="main__slide--introduction">
          <h3>Continuous Assessment</h3>
        </div>
        <!-- https://www.cigna.com/es-us/knowledge-center/hw/maniobra-de-heimlich-para-adultos-y-para-nios-de-tf7235-->
        <p>
          If the victim does not regain consciousness, continue with compressions until
          the emergency team arrives. If the person regains consciousness, place them on
          their side in the recovery position. This ensures that the airways are clear.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="main__slide--buttons">
